<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Detection - Process FMEA</title>
  <style>
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #aaa;
      padding: 8px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #ddd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Detection (Process FMEA)</h1>
  <p>Detection is an assessment of the likelihood that the best listed control will detect the failure mode during the process. It is a relative ranking within each individual FMEA. Lower detection ratings typically require improved control strategies.</p>
  <p>If more than one control exists, it's recommended to describe the detection rating alongside the control and record the lowest value in the detection column.</p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Pt.</th>
        <th>Opportunity for Detection</th>
        <th>Process Detection Control Description</th>
        <th>Detection Probability</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% datosDeteccion.forEach((item) => { %>
        <tr>
          <td><%= item.puntaje %></td>
          <td><%= item.oportunidad %></td>
          <td><%= item.descripcion %></td>
          <td><%= item.probabilidad %></td>
        </tr>
      <% }); %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
